Science Superpowers is a reimplementation of the architecture of Superpowers
(https://github.com/obra/superpowers) by Jesse Vincent, adapted from a
software-development methodology to a computational-science methodology.

Superpowers is MIT licensed. The skill content in this repository is original;
the plugin-packaging mechanics, including the session-start bootstrap hook,
multi-harness manifests, and version-sync tooling, are modeled on that project.
